<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
        <title>Contact</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contact-style.css" type="text/css" media="all">
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>Contact me</h1>
            <a id="button" href="/en">Home</a>
        </header>

        <main>
            <p>I am interested in an opportunity to work as a web developer. If you would like to ask a question, arrange an interview or give me a suggestion, feel free to use the message box below. Thank you!</p>
            <form id="form" action="https://formsubmit.co/dalima.dev@gmail.com" method="POST">
                
                    <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="Name" required>
                    <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="E-mail" required>
                    <textarea id="message" type="text" name="message" id="message" placeholder="Type your message here..."  required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Send</button>
            </form>
        </main>

        <footer>
